Here is the CSS code that you can use to achieve these styles:

```css
.titleBar {
    background-color: orange;
    border-bottom: 1px solid black;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: small;
    padding: 5px;
    user-select: none; /* This will prevent text selection */
}

/* This will apply styles to all buttons inside titleBar */
.titleBar button {
    border: 1px solid black;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: small;
    border-radius: 2px; /* This will give rounded corners */
}

```
